Iteration:
    Repeats the same procedure multiple times untill it reaches a specified endpoint

Loop:
    Code that iterates, move from beginning to end of the process, then strating over

-> to write code that iterates you need:
1. Specify the data that beginning iterated through
2. What should happen to data during each iteration
3. Indicate when the loop should stop

Infinte Loop:
    Bug that can occur when the ending condition is omitted or specifed incorrectly